Entries.default: "This is why you don't neglect your chores."
"It's like a model of Neketaka. Pretty up top, ugly below."
"I admit it is beyond my expertise, but this looks... unwell."
"Ain't cities got regulations 'gainst this sort of place? No?"
"The sanctum is looking wetter than usual, I say."
"How long do you reckon it takes for a place to end up like this?"
